# V2 User Guide

## Use Case
Java merge conflicts after pull/merge.

## Prompt

Use Merge Conflict Agent.
Current branch: feature/payment
Merged develop.
Balanced mode.

## What Happens

1. Detect conflicted files
2. Use Bitbucket-CLI metadata
3. Resolve safe conflicts
4. Ask user on risky files
5. Run compile
6. Generate CSV logs

## Outputs

Reports folder:
before.csv
actions.csv
after.csv
summary.md
